title: NORDUN Lined Notebook A5 Thick Journal,366 Pages Notebooks for Writing,100gsm Paper Hardcover Leather Journal for Office School Work Women Men,Sticky Tabs,14.5 x 21cm - Purple
features: 【366 Pages/183 Sheets】:This A5 notebook,with a 7mm spacing,is a classic university standard notebook that provides ample writing space for you. Multiple colors to meet your needs in various occasions. Each journal notebook comes with colored index stickers for easy categorization and organization of content.

【100GSM Premium Paper】:The A5 journal is made of 100GSM high grid paper, which is 20% thicker than regular paper. The paper is smooth and the writing is fluent, the ink does not leak out, and it is suitable for most pens. The 180 ° flat design makes reading and writing more convenient and comfortable.

【Exquisite Leather Cover】:The leather notebook cover is designed with inspiration from the "Tree of Knowledge". Using a unique embossing process, raised textures are created to give the patterns a realistic tactile feel. The sturdy hard cover makes lined notebooks more durable and comfortable to the touch, helping to protect the pages inside and providing a comfortable writing surface.

【Perfect Design】:A5 hardback notebook has 4 directory pages, which can record more entries; 2 ribbon bookmarks for quick access to important content; The expandable inner pocket on the back can store notes, business cards, receipts, appointment cards, etc; use elastic bands to close the cover, and the pen holder ring can fix the pen.

【Wide Usage】 :This A5 journal notebook is very suitable for home, office, and school use. It can be used as a personal notebook, diary notebook, business and work notebook, to-do list notebook etc,making it the perfect gift for loved ones, friends, family, or colleagues.
